      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 18:51:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡周一会见特朗普，谈论伊朗加沙的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/netanyahu-to-meet-trump-on-monday-to-talk-tariffs-gaza-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列官员说，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）将于周一与华盛顿总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）开会，以寻求更好的关税协议，并讨论加沙的战争，叙利亚和伊朗核计划的局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/netanyahu-to-meet-trump-on-monday-to-talk-tariffs-gaza-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 18:13:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克希望我们，欧洲搬到零及其自由贸易区域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/musk-hopes-us-europe-will-move-to-zero-tariff-free-trade-zone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）希望在美国和欧洲之间建立“零及其及其贸易区”之间的“零关税”制度，这将有效地创建“自由贸易区”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/musk-hopes-us-europe-will-move-to-zero-tariff-free-trade-zone</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 16:51:16 GMT</pubDate>
